</h2><h2 id="coding-in-the-kitchen-how-devin-davies-whipped-up-the-tasty-recipe-app-crouton-1">Coding in the kitchen: How Devin Davies whipped up the tasty recipe app Crouton
</h2><p>November 4, 2024</p>
<p><img alt="An illustration of a kitchen with teal walls and white cabinets. Two Apple Vision Pro screens float above a stove, on which sits a pot and pan." loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="/rss/downloaded_images/f68c91097aa8468a5465305fe6c4cc31.jpeg"></p>
